data.title: Disputed Barricade: The Life And Times Of Josip Broz-tito, Marshal Of Yugoslavia by Fitzroy Maclean: Good (1957)
data.meta_description: Hardcover - Jonathan Cape - 1957 - Condition: Good - Dust Jacket Included - 1957. 480 pages. Beige jacket over green cloth with gilt lettering. Inscription to front endpaper. Pages are lightly tanned and thumbed at the edges, with light foxing. Binding has remained firm. Boards are a little rub worn, slight shelf wear to corners, spine and edges. Corners are a little bumped. Spine ends are mildly crushed. Light tanning to spine and edges. Light wear to unclipped dust jacket with tears, nicks and creases to spine, edge and corners. Light tanning to spine and edges. - Disputed Barricade: The Life And Times Of Josip Broz-tito, Marshal Of Yugoslavia
